	Choose work that you're passionate about.
	Play to your strengths. Choose work that allows you to spend 80% of the time in a good fit with the way you are wired. (For example, Jesse most enjoys creative work and interacting with other people, with about a 50/50 split on solo work vs. team work. He is good at detailed and management work too, but if that consumes the majority of his work time, he gets burned out.)
