		<title>MCR-022: The First 90 Days of the Rest of Your Life</title>
		<link>http://www.mancaveradio.com/mcr-022-the-first-90-days-of-the-rest-of-your-life/</link>
		<comments>http://www.mancaveradio.com/mcr-022-the-first-90-days-of-the-rest-of-your-life/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 05 Apr 2012 18:25:54 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>cave@mancaveradio.com (Jesse and J. J. Lahey)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Listen to the Show]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.mancaveradio.com/?p=911</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[“Enjoying now” while visiting in-laws in Washington DC. 7 Reasons You Should Learn Karate (or, How I Got My Butt Kicked by a Girl). Interview with speaker and author Kent Julian. Planning to get the most out of life and work in the second quarter of 2012. Taking a Family of 6 Across the Country [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p><em><a href="http://www.mancaveradio.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/90_v2.jpg"><img class="alignright  wp-image-920" title="The First 90 Days of the Rest of Your Life" src="http://www.mancaveradio.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/90_v2.jpg" alt="The First 90 Days of the Rest of Your Life" width="218" height="211" /></a>“Enjoying now” while visiting in-laws in Washington DC. 7 Reasons You Should Learn Karate (or, How I Got My Butt Kicked by a Girl). Interview with speaker and author Kent Julian. Planning to get the most out of life and work in the second quarter of 2012.</em></p>
<h2>Taking a Family of 6 Across the Country to See In-Laws Is a Recipe for &#8230; Fun?</h2>
<p>Last week, our family was on vacation with Jesse’s in-laws in Washington, D. C. (and as a result, we didn’t do a show that week). Traveling halfway across the country for a family reunion may not top everyone’s list for fun, but we turned a good time into a great time by putting the “Enjoy Now” practice into use.</p>
<h2>Why You Should Learn Karate</h2>
<p>After taking a week off while on vacation, Jesse was ready to kick it again at his karate class — instead he got kicked in the face by a teenage girl with a black belt! He kicked her butt in retaliation. Literally. Unfortunately, that&#8217;s as high as he could kick, and the butt zone doesn&#8217;t score a point in karate sparring.</p>
<p>Still, after all is said and done, Jesse has some valid reasons for why karate is a great cross-training sport for the average guy. For more about the story, and the list of reasons, check out his blog post, <a title="7 Reasons You Should Learn Karate (or, How I Got My Butt Kicked by a Girl)" href="http://www.mancaveradio.com/7-reasons-you-should-learn-karate-or-how-i-got-my-butt-kicked-by-a-girl/">7 Reasons You Should Learn Karate (or, How I Got My Butt Kicked by a Girl)</a>.</p>
<h2>Interview with Kent Julian</h2>
<p>Our good friend <a href="http://www.kentjulian.com/">Kent Julian</a> discusses how he became a successful speaker and author — even though he wasn’t already famous. He shares an important lesson for every guy trying to make it in competitive field.</p>
<p>Information about Kent’s career-coaching services is available at <a href="http://www.liveitforward.com/">www.liveitforward.com</a>, and more about his training for up-and-coming speakers is available at <a href="http://www.speakitforward.com/">www.speakitforward.com</a>.</p>
<h2>The First 90 Days of the Rest of Your Life</h2>
<p>At the start of the year, the guys set goals for the first quarter. Now it’s time to check in and see how they did and what they’re going to do differently in the next quarter.</p>
<div class="shr-publisher-911"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><div class='shareaholic-like-buttonset' style='float:none;height:30px;'><a class='shareaholic-fblike' data-shr_layout='button_count' data-shr_showfaces='false' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mancaveradio.com%2Fmcr-022-the-first-90-days-of-the-rest-of-your-life%2F' data-shr_title='MCR-022%3A+The+First+90+Days+of+the+Rest+of+Your+Life'></a><a class='shareaholic-googleplusone' data-shr_size='medium' data-shr_count='true' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mancaveradio.com%2Fmcr-022-the-first-90-days-of-the-rest-of-your-life%2F' data-shr_title='MCR-022%3A+The+First+90+Days+of+the+Rest+of+Your+Life'></a><a class='shareaholic-tweetbutton' data-shr_count='horizontal' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mancaveradio.com%2Fmcr-022-the-first-90-days-of-the-rest-of-your-life%2F' data-shr_title='MCR-022%3A+The+First+90+Days+of+the+Rest+of+Your+Life'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><div class="feedflare">
