		<title>MCR-012: Ordinary Men, Extraordinary Lives (featuring Dr. Jim Sharon)</title>
		<link>http://www.mancaveradio.com/mcr-012-ordinary-men-extraordinary-lives-featuring-dr-jim-sharon/</link>
