<h2><strong>UberMan: Uber Showdown</strong></h2>
<p>Using the Mayor as bait, UberMan sets the ultimate trap in an attempt to capture four super-villains at once: Quick and Qwack, The Jesster, and a phantom that he can’t recognize but who has appeared in past episodes.</p>
