		<item>
		<title>MCR-005: Roadkill &amp; Bucket Lists</title>
		<link>http://www.mancaveradio.com/nov-30-2011-man-cave-radio/</link>
		<comments>http://www.mancaveradio.com/nov-30-2011-man-cave-radio/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 03 Dec 2011 14:23:50 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>cave@mancaveradio.com (Jesse and J. J. Lahey)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Listen to the Show]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.mancaveradio.com/?p=272</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Interview with Tony Elam, bellman at the Gaylord Palms Hotel in Orlando. A fresh look back at the movie “Bucket List.” Winning with Kids: Who has it better than we do? Up close and personal with roadkill. Man Toys: glass multi-touch keyboard and mouse, plus the 2012 Jeep Wrangler. Wimpmaker Alert: should guys be concerned [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p><em><a href="http://www.mancaveradio.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/TonyElam.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-277" title="Tony Elam" src="http://www.mancaveradio.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/TonyElam.jpg" alt="Tony Elam" width="210" height="186" /></a>Interview with Tony Elam, bellman at the Gaylord Palms Hotel in Orlando. A fresh look back at the movie “Bucket List.” Winning with Kids: Who has it better than we do? Up close and personal with roadkill. Man Toys: glass multi-touch keyboard and mouse, plus the 2012 Jeep Wrangler. Wimpmaker Alert: should guys be concerned about a level playing field? SportsMan: New head football coach at Ohio State, plus Tony Stewart wins NASCAR championship. Man Hero: Ernest Shackleton. Marriage Moment: He says, She says. UberMan meets The Jesster.</em></p>
<h2><strong>A Fresh Look Back at the Movie “Bucket List”</strong></h2>
<p>We finally got around to checking out this movie that is on the top of list of many guys for fun, inspirational flicks. The very next day, Phil Cooke happened to mention the same movie &#8230; but he asked if you <a href="http://philcooke.com/do-you-have-a-bucket-list-of-people-to-see-before-you-die/" target="_blank">have a list of PEOPLE</a> you&#8217;d like to meet or talk to before you die.</p>
<h2><strong>Winning with Kids</strong></h2>
<p>We’re inspired by the example of Cody Gascho who teaches his junior-high basketball players how to answer the question, “Who has it better than we do? “</p>
<h2><strong>On the Hunt</strong></h2>
<p>Jesse gets up close and personal with roadkill. Zach and J. J. can’t stay awake long enough to bag a deer.</p>
<h2><strong>Man Toys</strong></h2>
<p>We get geeked out by the possibilities with a next-gen, glass <a href="http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1116966310/multi-touch-keyboard-and-mouse" target="_blank">multi-touch keyboard and mouse</a>. Jesse shares his long-time idea for an even more advanced laser keyboard for smart phones.</p>
<p>The <a href="http://www.mensjournal.com/the-wrangler-rejuvenated" target="_blank">2012 Jeep Wrangler</a> has us pretty stoked too. It’s a jeep for the 21<sup>st</sup> century with more power and 20+ MPG.</p>
<h2><strong>Men At Work</strong></h2>
<p>Tony Elam, from the Gaylord Palms Hotel in Orlando, explains how being a bellman for 12 years has trained his entrepreneurial skills. He’s begun sharing his accumulated wisdom at <a href="http://findingforwardmotion.com" target="_blank">http://findingforwardmotion.com</a>.</p>
<h2><strong>Wimpmaker Alert</strong></h2>
<p>Should guys be concerned about a level playing field? We don’t think guys should be worried about new competition, but we should continue to look for opportunities to use our “man gifts” to make a positive difference for customers, our families, and our communities. Otherwise, the future of America could look a lot like many third-world countries, where many people seem to think that men only cause problems rather than create solutions. We mentioned articles by <a href="http://www.xyonline.net/content/what%E2%80%99s-real-%E2%80%9Cboy-crisis%E2%80%9D-they-will-soon-find-themselves-having-compete-girls-truly-level-pla" target="_blank">Bill Patrick</a> and <a href="http://www.cnn.com/2011/11/30/opinion/gates-maternal-health/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 " target="_blank">Melinda Gates</a>.</p>
<h2><strong>SportsMan: Ty Daniels</strong></h2>
<p>Ohio State University hires Urban Meyer as its football coach. Tony Stewart Wins NASCAR Championship at Homestead.</p>
<h2><strong>Man Hero</strong></h2>
<p><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Shackleton" target="_blank">Ernest Shackleton</a> was one of the <a href="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/nova/shackleton/1914/team.html" target="_blank">key explorers</a> of Antartica in the early 1900s. Even his rivals admitted that he was a great leader. “If I am in the devil of a hole and want to get out of it, give me Shackleton every time.&#8221;</p>
<p>Put in <a href="http://www.cnn.com/SPECIALS/cnn.heroes/index.html" target="_blank">your vote</a> a hero of today at CNN.</p>
<h2><strong>Marriage Moment</strong></h2>
<p>Jesse plays a game of “He Says, She Says” with Erin.</p>
<h2><strong>UberMan Meets The Jesster</strong></h2>
<p>UberMan demonstrates how to be an effective bellman, but The Jesster has something to say (or sing?) about that.</p>
<div class="shr-publisher-272"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><div class='shareaholic-like-buttonset' style='float:none;height:30px;'><a class='shareaholic-fblike' data-shr_layout='button_count' data-shr_showfaces='false' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mancaveradio.com%2Fnov-30-2011-man-cave-radio%2F' data-shr_title='MCR-005%3A+Roadkill+%26+Bucket+Lists'></a><a class='shareaholic-googleplusone' data-shr_size='medium' data-shr_count='true' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mancaveradio.com%2Fnov-30-2011-man-cave-radio%2F' data-shr_title='MCR-005%3A+Roadkill+%26+Bucket+Lists'></a><a class='shareaholic-tweetbutton' data-shr_count='horizontal' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mancaveradio.com%2Fnov-30-2011-man-cave-radio%2F' data-shr_title='MCR-005%3A+Roadkill+%26+Bucket+Lists'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><div class="feedflare">
