		<title>MCR-004: Why Won’t My Wife Have Sex With Me?</title>
		<link>http://www.mancaveradio.com/nov-23-2011-man-cave-radio/</link>
		<comments>http://www.mancaveradio.com/nov-23-2011-man-cave-radio/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 24 Nov 2011 15:55:40 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>cave@mancaveradio.com (Jesse and J. J. Lahey)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Listen to the Show]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.mancaveradio.com/?p=241</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Interview with Laymon Hicks, motivational speaker for high-school and college students. JJ needs a motivational speaker himself. Ty Daniels gets us ready for the Ohio State v. Michigan Game. Man Toys: Porter-Cable 18v Infrared Thermometer and Nissan Juke-R. Matthew Casteel becomes king of the road. How to cook a Thanksgiving dinner. Charlie asks, “Why won’t [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p><em><a href="http://www.mancaveradio.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/LaymonHicks.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-243" title="Laymon Hicks" src="http://www.mancaveradio.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/LaymonHicks.png" alt="Laymon Hicks" width="232" height="250" /></a>Interview with Laymon Hicks, motivational speaker for high-school and college students. JJ needs a motivational speaker himself. Ty Daniels gets us ready for the Ohio State v. Michigan Game. Man Toys: Porter-Cable 18v Infrared Thermometer and Nissan Juke-R. Matthew Casteel becomes king of the road. How to cook a Thanksgiving dinner. Charlie asks, “Why won’t my wife have sex with me?” UberMan gets motivational.</em></p>
<h2><strong>J. J. Needs a Motivational Speaker</strong></h2>
<p>Jesse realizes that J. J. is distracted and needs to focus more on accomplishing his life’s purpose. So he brings in a pro to knock some sense into him.</p>
<h2><strong>Ready for the Ohio State v. Michigan Game</strong></h2>
<p>Rabid Buckeye fan Ty Daniels is permitted to enter the Man Cave’s Wolverine territory in order to share background for the big game this coming Saturday … perhaps the most exciting game of the past decade between these two archrivals.</p>
<h2><strong>Man Toys</strong></h2>
<p><em>Porter-Cable 18v Infrared Thermometer</em></p>
<p>As featured in Popular Mechanic’s <a href="http://www.popularmechanics.com/technology/gadgets/tools/popular-mechanics-cant-miss-holiday-gift-guide-for-2011#ixzz1eSFWvUNr" target="blank">Can&#8217;t-Miss Holiday Gift Guide for 2011 &#8211; Gadget Gifts for Men</a>, this baby can find insulation gaps or measure a grill&#8217;s heat. What guy doesn’t need a $60 thermometer?</p>
<p><em>Nissan Juke-R</em><em></em></p>
<p>As featured on <a href="http://uncrate.com/stuff/nissan-juke-r/" target="blank">Uncrate</a>, this tiny monster has so much power that it must practically fly off the ground.</p>
<h2><strong>It Started</strong></h2>
<p>A brief clip from one of our favorite comedians and speakers, <a href="http://www.kendavis.com/" target="blank">Ken Davis</a>.</p>
<h2><strong>King of the Road</strong></h2>
<p>Matthew Casteel – songwriter, father of six, youth minister, and owner of Simple VA Solutions – spent 10 months living a dream that many guys have. He and his wife sold their house, bought a camper, and traveled the country with their kids.</p>
<h2><strong>How to Cook a Thanksgiving Dinner</strong></h2>
<p>Just in case you were wondering how to keep your family happy and impress the hottie next door.</p>
<h2><strong>Men At Work</strong></h2>
<p>Living his dream at the age of 24, <a href="http://www.laymonhicks.com/" target="blank">Laymon Hicks</a> is a full-time motivational speaker who inspires high-school and college students around the nation. He believes “you can make a living, and live your making.” But how did someone so young, with no “connections,” succeed in a role that typically requires many years of “paying your dues”?</p>
<h2><strong>Marriage Moment</strong></h2>
<p><em>Charlie asks, “Why won’t my wife have sex with me?” </em></p>
<p>In the aftermath of the birth of his first child, Charlie’s efforts to Jump On It haven’t been scoring with his wife. See <a href="http://goodmenproject.com/featured-content/why-wont-my-wife-have-sex-with-me/" target="blank">http://goodmenproject.com/featured-content/why-wont-my-wife-have-sex-with-me/</a></p>
<h2><strong>UberMan Gets Motivational</strong></h2>
<p>UberMan shows off his public-speaking skills, but the Mayor is beside himself.</p>
