Charlie asks, “Why won’t my wife have sex with me?” 

In the aftermath of the birth of his first child, Charlie’s efforts to Jump On It haven’t been scoring with his wife. See http://goodmenproject.com/featured-content/why-wont-my-wife-have-sex-with-me/
UberMan Gets Motivational
UberMan shows off his public-speaking skills, but the Mayor is beside himself.</itunes:summary>
