		<description><![CDATA[Our first pre-launch show! Wow, we really sucked. We even made ourselves bored. But nonetheless, it was fun to record this in the brand-new man cave of Marty Lahey, owner of Manhattans Restaurant in Toledo, Ohio, and second-best dad in the world (#1 being Jesse). See www.manhattanstoledo.com We talked about what it’s like to own [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p>Our first pre-launch show!</p>
<p>Wow, we really sucked. We even made ourselves bored.</p>
<p>But nonetheless, it was fun to record this in the brand-new man cave of Marty Lahey, owner of Manhattans Restaurant in Toledo, Ohio, and second-best dad in the world (#1 being Jesse). See <a title="Manhattans Toledo" href="www.manhattanstoledo.com">www.manhattanstoledo.com</a></p>
<p>We talked about what it’s like to own a restaurant, and also discussed Marty’s experience going from near-couch-potato to sprint-triathlete and half-marathoner, despite the fact that he’s already on AARP’s mailing list.</p>
