Wow, we really sucked. We even made ourselves bored.

But nonetheless, it was fun to record this in the brand-new man cave of Marty Lahey, owner of Manhattans Restaurant in Toledo, Ohio, and second-best dad in the world (#1 being Jesse). See www.manhattanstoledo.com

We talked about what it’s like to own a restaurant, and also discussed Marty’s experience going from near-couch-potato to sprint-triathlete and half-marathoner, despite the fact that he’s already on AARP’s mailing list.</itunes:summary>
